http://www.savers.org:80/mrc/medianomics/octjapan.html 204.71.237.73 19970108061209 text/html 2869
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:12:19 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 22-Jul-96 18:22:04 GMT
Content-length: 2683
