<DOCNO>WT16-B35-83</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000242-B027-188</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/mrc/medianomics/octjobs.html 204.71.237.73 19970108061220 text/html 4180
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:12:37 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 22-Jul-96 18:22:09 GMT
Content-length: 3994
