http://www.savers.org:80/nationalreview/29july96/week.html 204.71.237.73 19970108064433 text/html 16400
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:44:49 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 19-Jul-96 15:29:36 GMT
