<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/nationalreview/15july96/rusty.html 204.71.237.73 19970108064619 text/html 5323
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:46:34 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 19:58:40 GMT
